  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Change in baseline of Pain</measure>
    <time_frame>base line (moment of inclusion), day 15th, day 45th and in the last day of the sessions of rTMS (4X in two months)</time_frame>
    <description>assessing by Visual Analog Scale for Pain (VAS). This scale range from 0 (no pain) to 10 (maximum pain), being considered an effective improvement in the patient's pain when the pain decreases at least in 30% from the basal score.</description>
